{"tid":1931270,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS Plus送Monster Hunter World?","createTime":"2020-03-18T05:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T16:41:35.000Z","uid":188176,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0595ae5ed305f0e2aa178ffb7772b80378ca6ae5","tid":1931270,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:39:18.000Z","msg":"CAPCOM 製作，2018 年 1 月推出的 PS4 狩獵動作遊戲《魔物獵人 世界（Monster hunter World）》，今（18）日起在 PlayStation Store 開放 PlayStation Plus 會員免費下載遊玩，期限至 4 月 22 日止。<br />\n<br />\n在大型擴充資料片《魔物獵人 世界：Iceborne》推出的帶動下，《魔物獵人 世界》目前累計銷售已經超過 1500 萬套。今日官方無預警將《魔物獵人 世界》開放為 PS Plus 免費遊戲，<span style=\"color: red;\">凡是 PS Plus 會員的玩家都可以在 3 月 18 日至 4 月 22 日期間免費下載遊玩。而且與一般 PS Plus 免費遊戲一樣，玩家只要在開放下載期間曾下載過遊戲或是曾將遊戲加入內容保存庫過，就可以在 PS Plus 會員資格有效期間繼續免費暢玩。</span>"},{"pid":"b8f4ee02b9f4a316ca789d50ebcc5469d8f1b42d","tid":1931270,"uid":7043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"本身有碟<br />\n唔知down左會唔會唔洗入碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571d58738c6563ae6936afc66abfbc6462f4f2d7","tid":1931270,"uid":10422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"當capcom不再capcoin <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05d2277bcadc73fd83aaf468e1578edfe0c6c9a","tid":1931270,"uid":141078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f4ee02b9f4a316ca789d50ebcc5469d8f1b42d","tid":1931270,"uid":7043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"本身有碟<br />\n唔知down左會唔會唔洗入碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"理論上係"},{"pid":"2eacd5f1082a3fcc3f78a9cb9e6512dd6935544b","tid":1931270,"uid":116197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8f4ee0